-- BCP Polish arm Millennium Q1 net profit rises by 30 pct
-- By Marcin Goclowski
-- Mon Apr 28, 2014 02:11AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, April 28 (Reuters) - Polish lender Millennium <MILP.WA> reported a 30-percent rise in its first-quarter net profits, exactly in line with market forecasts, thanks to higher net income margin and fees, it said on Monday.

